{"tid":942990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[The Hunt]熟女約會後謊報強姦　被害男崩潰罹患憂鬱","createTime":"2018-12-16T08:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T09:03:26.000Z","uid":122,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4728e1f658b36f36a48bed90356270d60e65283b","tid":942990,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181216/640_6cb7bf25848fdb5b7498cfd8c6431ebb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181216%2F640_6cb7bf25848fdb5b7498cfd8c6431ebb.jpg&h=0af431d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國諾福克郡（Norfolk）一名35歲的女子，去年透過約會網站「Plenty of Fish」認識一名58歲男子後，到對方家中過夜，隔天偷走男子3,040英鎊（約11.8萬元台幣）。她被捕後一開始辯稱，這筆錢是男子給她的援交費，後來她改口謊稱自己被對方強姦，最後她才承認偷竊，周三（12日）被判刑20個月。被害的男子表示，自己「被控」強姦後，不但身敗名裂，也因為受到極大的壓力，罹患憂鬱症。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181216/640_9e8f88db1af8564ed8bf23e4fd822f5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181216%2F640_9e8f88db1af8564ed8bf23e4fd822f5b.jpg&h=cac35e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女子里弗斯（Natalie Rivers）於去年12月，到男子家過夜，隔天她趁被害人外出期間，偷走3,040英鎊。里弗斯被捕後，最初辯稱，男子是她的「甜心老爸」（Sugar Daddy），這筆錢是援交費用，每小時收費150英鎊（約5824元台幣），但後來她改口稱，自己是被迫性交，遭到強姦。警方花了4個月的時間蒐證，才拆穿她的謊言，她坦承偷竊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181216/640_c59b082a6146cc63e9bdda4852614e05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181216%2F640_c59b082a6146cc63e9bdda4852614e05.jpg&h=f90932c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被害人在聲明中表示，警方花了4個月才證實他的清白，而在他被里弗斯指控強姦後，受到極大的壓力，罹患憂鬱症，身體也出了毛病。<br />\n<br />\n里弗斯早有多次透過約會，趁機偷竊的前科，2013年她曾偷走約會對象的支票簿及信用卡， 她也曾用多個化名，假冒女警或退役女兵。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"94b814dbcf195569a14bad7ffeca669bce05cab0","tid":942990,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"我絕對没有強姦母豬.jpg"},{"pid":"1dc2c5490048221ce6a7847635c02b12d4eb9621","tid":942990,"uid":45120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"94b814dbcf195569a14bad7ffeca669bce05cab0","tid":942990,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"我絕對没有強姦母豬.jpg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:12:00.000Z","msg":"没<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6744ee32a41b8e5fa87bbf2798be9f45a7847963","tid":942990,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:24:47.000Z","msg":"Me too"},{"pid":"ba70ac4361cfa16d53ed0db433b5bb64544b48b8","tid":942990,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"其實全世界係咪應該立法有企圖明屈me too 屬於刑事罪行<br />\n<br />\n當然我係講緊有證據嗰啲"},{"pid":"16534b80aa6797e28278d6f893098b4bae9b0009","tid":942990,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba70ac4361cfa16d53ed0db433b5bb64544b48b8","tid":942990,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"其實全世界係咪應該立法有企圖明屈me too 屬於刑事罪行<br />\n<br />\n當然我係講緊有證據嗰啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"女權：咁會令真正的受害者唔敢企出黎 怕比人話自己屈人強姦<br />\n<br />\n而家應該可以用妨礙司法公正告屈人metoo的人？"},{"pid":"639acfb390570b410db82a20043af661d527d1c9","tid":942990,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16534b80aa6797e28278d6f893098b4bae9b0009","tid":942990,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba70ac4361cfa16d53ed0db433b5bb64544b48b8","tid":942990,"uid":143499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"其實全世界係咪應該立法有企圖明屈me too 屬於刑事罪行<br />\n<br />\n當然我係講緊有證據嗰啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"女權：咁會令真正的受害者唔敢企出黎 怕比人話自己屈人強姦<br />\n<br />\n而家應該可以用妨礙司法公正告屈人metoo的人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T08:49:02.000Z","msg":"試過屈強姦， 查返whatsapp wechat紀錄係你情我願 ，cctv影埋一齊 入酒店大堂一齊搭